original: Öcken, Gustaf Hjalmar, disponent, Göteborg, f. 29/6/81 i Gillberga, Värml. 1. — Anst. v. A. F. Hagströms Vin-handel i Kungsör, Gillberga, Motala o. Östhammar 96-06, Vinimport A-B i Sthlm 07-17, A-B Vin- & Spritcentralen i resp. Sthlm, Sundsvall o. Gbg sed. 17. RVO, PatrGM.
translated: Öcken, Gustaf Hjalmar, manager, Gothenburg, b. 29/6/81 in Gillberga, Värmland. 1. — Employed by A. F. Hagström's Wine Trade in Kungsör, Gillberga, Motala and Östhammar from 96-06, Vinimport A-B in Stockholm from 07-17, A-B Vin- & Spiritscentralen in Stockholm, Sundsvall and Gothenburg since 17. Knight of the Royal Order of Vasa, Patriotic Merit Medal.

award.name: Knight of the Royal Order of Vasa
